---
---
<section class="section deploy" id="deploy">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="copy">
        <span class="eyebrow">Deploy</span>
        <h2>Productive in an afternoon. Boring forever.</h2>
        <p class="lede">
          One static Rust binary with an embedded UI. SQLite by default needs zero external
          services; switch the database URL to Postgres and add stateless replicas to scale out.
          Kubernetes is supported, never required.
        </p>
        <dl class="points">
          <div class="point">
            <dt>Local</dt>
            <dd>One <code>docker run</code> or a native binary on macOS/Linux.</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="point">
            <dt>Internal</dt>
            <dd>The same image on ECS/EC2 behind an ALB, Postgres for state, stateless replicas.</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="point">
            <dt>Identity</dt>
            <dd>OIDC out of the box; SAML/SCIM, multi-tenant, SIEM streaming behind trait seams.</dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </div>

      <div class="code">
        <div class="code-bar">
          <span class="code-title">~/frontkeep · onboarding</span>
        </div>
<pre><span class="c"># 1 · run it</span>
<span class="p">$</span> docker run -p 8080:8080 <span class="o">frontkeep</span> serve

<span class="c"># 2 · register the project (the gate)</span>
<span class="p">$</span> frontkeep project register \
    --name <span class="s">"Fraud Detection"</span> --owner <span class="s">you@corp.example</span> \
    --manager <span class="s">lead@corp.example</span> --group <span class="s">platform</span> \
    --classification <span class="s">poc</span> --budget-usd <span class="o">100</span>
  <span class="o">→ minted proj-2026-0042</span>

<span class="c"># 3 · point your agent at the MCP front door</span>
<span class="p">$</span> claude mcp add --transport http frontkeep \
    http://localhost:8080/mcp --header <span class="s">"Authorization: Bearer $FRONTKEEP_PAT"</span></pre>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .deploy .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 56px; align-items: start; }
  .deploy h2 { font-size: 32px; line-height: 1.15; margin: 16px 0 16px; max-width: 22ch; }
  .points { margin: 24px 0 0; padding: 0; }
  .point { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 90px 1fr; gap: 16px; padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line); }
  .point:last-child { border-bottom: 0; }
  .point dt { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 12px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.04em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--fg-faint); padding-top: 2px; }
  .point dd { margin: 0; color: var(--fg-muted); font-size: 14.5px; line-height: 1.5; }
  .point dd code { background: var(--panel); border: 1px solid var(--line); padding: 1px 5px; border-radius: 3px; color: var(--fg); }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .deploy .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 36px; }
    .deploy h2 { font-size: 26px; }
  }
</style>
